    "rationale": "Overall credibility assessment accepted. Twelve of thirteen V&V 40 factors meet or exceed required levels. The single deficiency in Test conditions (achieved level 1 vs. required level 2) is accepted given mandatory ASTM F1717 standardization to a single quasi-static loading rate and the corroborating agreement across all three QoIs (E/uval < 1.96, percentage difference < 10%). The FEA modeling framework is assessed as sufficiently credible to support the regulatory submission decision.",
